# CG Milestone Checklist Protocol App

This is a multi-user checklist protocol app built with Streamlit, based on the CG Milestone Process Outline.

## Features
- User login
- Interactive checklist per logistics bucket
- Timestamped logs
- Log viewer per user

## Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/cg-checklist-app.git
   cd cg-checklist-app
pip install -r requirements.txt
